com.jamejam.api.types

Class Document

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jamejam.api.types.Document

  • public class Document
extends Object
    This object represents a general file (as opposed to photos (PhotoSize) and audio (Audio) files). Any getters labeled optional might return a default value (such as null).
